Small tree based calculation engine. To be extended with visual tools and grid framework later.

See file LICENSE for licensing details.

Currently only a quite rudimentary prototype is implemented. Two sheet functions,
spartanic console GUI to edit sheets.

This is build on haskell platform March 2011, with ghc 7.
For compilation you should additionally have the cabal packages

-hlint (optional, for make hlint)
-test-framwork and test-framework-quickcheck2 (optional, for make test)
-QuickCheck in version >= 2 (already part of Haskell platform?)
